                      activeMsg.name || "-"
                    }\nالهاتف: ${activeMsg.phone || "-"}\nالقناة: ${
                      activeMsg.channel || "-"
                    }\nالتاريخ: ${fmtDate(activeMsg.createdAt) || "-"}\n\n${
                      activeMsg.message || ""
